    "During delensing, if f dl is independent of ℓ, the estimation of r remains unbiased.",
    "Typically, A L < 1.",
    "However, if f dl heavily depends on ℓ, we can adjust the parameterization to:C ℓ = rC tens ℓ (r = 1) + A L C len,th ℓ + N del ℓ + N BB ℓ.",
    "(2.40)The estimation of N del ℓ is obtained from simulations.",
    "The uncertainty of r can be roughly expressed as:σ(r = 0) = l (2l + 1)f sky 2 C tens l (r = 1) f dl C len l + N BB l 2 -1/2."
